attributes.title: Beautiful flower
attributes.description: Flowers are also called the bloom or blossom of a plant. Flowers have petals. Inside the part of the flower that has petals are the parts which produce pollen and seeds. ... Flowers may grow separately on the plant, or they may grow together in an inflorescence.
